title: MOTOROLA UNLOCKING TOOL.USB-Smart Cyclone P2K Easy Tool 5.3 Fixe
description:
Cyclone P2K Easy Tool features:

Direct unlock all Neptune LTE based models, up to 08.0A bootloader.
Bootloader 08.0A and higher via test point.
Direct unlock ? all Neptune ULS based models.
Direct unlock ? all Neptune LT based models.
Direct unlock ? all Neptune LTE2 based models (Motorola V360, V7, U6) using testpoints.
Direct unlock ? all Rainbow POG, with Micron and Intel flash chips, without opening up to 0.6.3.1 bootloader version, higher via testpoint.
Lock to network any of supported models.
Backup and restore boot loader and PDS zone.
Flashing 1FF (SHX) original files.
Flashing full backups of binary files.
Flex using original HS files (including file system).
Automatic PDS repair on most models, not need any other write operation, all is made automatically.
Boot loader repair, 0x1DE, 0xDAB and other nasty error messages produced by partial or permanent damage in boot or PDS zone.
Can repair Motorola L6 and U6 killed by other software.

Access to most complete colection of Motorola P2K flash, flex
